data.description: Presenting a breathtaking 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Douglasville, GA. This remarkable residence epitomizes the perfect blend of luxury and comfort, featuring a spacious living area, a gourmet kitchen adorned with state-of-the-art appliances, and an opulent master suite boasting a spa-inspired ensuite bathroom. With three additional bedrooms, there's ample space for family and guests to unwind. Step outside to discover a meticulously landscaped backyard, providing a serene retreat for relaxation. Additionally, this home offers the convenience of an unfinished basement, offering endless possibilities for customization and expansion. Conveniently located near amenities and attractions, this property offers a coveted lifestyle in a charming community.
